Come on! Come on!</i>

06:42.574 --> 06:45.646
Dumb piece of junk. No bars...

06:45.646 --> 06:49.047
No bars! No bars!

06:52.417 --> 06:57.621
- Did that help?
- No! It's just...

06:57.689 --> 07:03.998
- What if I never get back home?
- Oh! You're just really homesick.

07:04.033 --> 07:06.198
Duh! What'd you think?!

07:08.700 --> 07:10.926
No, it's okay.

07:11.510 --> 07:15.379
We're okay!
 Steven said the gems

07:15.414 --> 07:19.710
could be coming for us any day.
And, you know, until then,

07:19.778 --> 07:27.147
- I got your back.
- Sadie... do you ever get lonely...

07:27.182 --> 07:30.618
even when you're around people?

07:34.140 --> 07:37.228
<i>♪ Why don't you let yourself just be... ♪</i>

07:37.295 --> 07:40.442
- Steven!
- How long have you been watching us?!

07:40.477 --> 07:42.766
- Don't you know what privacy is?!
- People walk in

07:42.867 --> 07:45.219
and out of my room all the time.

07:45.220 --> 07:48.140
Ugh!
I'm gonna go start on the fire.

07:48.175 --> 07:53.061
Hey! You don't have to go!
We're kind of on our own schedule here!

07:55.130 --> 07:56.772
What the heck?!

07:58.277 --> 08:02.686
It's a... gem?

08:04.578 --> 08:07.189
Whoa, whoa, whoa!

08:10.059 --> 08:13.464
- We have to get out of here!
- Steven!

08:13.531 --> 08:17.725
- What was that thing?!
- It must be what the gems were looking for!

08:17.760 --> 08:21.500
It never left the island
at all! It's invisible.

08:21.535 --> 08:24.502
A big invisible thing is after us?!

08:24.537 --> 08:30.982
I ... I ... I want to go home!
I wanna go home!

08:35.448 --> 08:38.451
- This way!
- Okay!

08:41.342 --> 08:45.849
- It's the warp pad!
- Lars, come on! Let's go home!

08:48.428 --> 08:52.346
- You knew!
- Uh, guys?

08:52.381 --> 08:55.609
It's her fault we've been trapped here!

08:55.644 --> 09:02.061
- Wha-a-a-a-a-at?!
- Look, I panicked! I hid the warp pad!

09:02.096 --> 09:04.176
You were just gonna leave, but
I knew how much you really

09:04.244 --> 09:08.905
needed this! Why don't
you ever let me help you?!

09:08.940 --> 09:10.846
Help me? Are you insane?!

09:10.847 --> 09:15.087
You trapped me on an island
so you could come on to me!

09:16.703 --> 09:19.005
- Ow!
- You kissed me on the mouth!

09:19.006 --> 09:21.516
- No, I didn't!
- Guys, I want to be mad, too,

09:21.529 --> 09:23.905
but can we do it on the warp pad?!

09:23.940 --> 09:27.161
Lars! Oh, gosh.

09:52.756 --> 09:56.408
Sadie!
Use your fish-murdering skills!

10:02.674 --> 10:06.534
Go, Sadie!

10:22.177 --> 10:27.097
Oh. Oh, I got this!
The gems are gonna be so impressed.

10:27.132 --> 10:30.560
We captured
a gem all by ourselves!

10:30.993 --> 10:33.773
Sadie, you were amazing!

10:33.774 --> 10:39.334
Yeah, that was really great
how you, uh... s-saved me.

10:39.402 --> 10:41.392
